  • Class
    Description
    Controller
    The Controller class controls the user interface and handles events for the earthquake visualization application.

    CustomCircleMarkerLayer is a MapLayer that displays a red circle marker on the map.
    Earthquake
    This class represents an earthquake.
    EarthquakeData
    The EarthquakeData class represents a collection of earthquake data.
    MainApplication
    The MainApplication class is the entry point of the EarthquakeJavaFX application.
    Quality
    The Quality enum represents different qualities of earthquake information, indicating their trustworthiness.
    StringInt
    The StringInt class represents a string paired with an integer value.
    Type
    The Type enum represents different types of earthquakes.
